  "text": "Since ε here is arbitrary, I obtain that the left hand side of (4.1) is not less than the right hand side of (4.1). In order to obtain an upper bound for HD(K ω ) I shall need the following result, which is contained, essentially, in [CITATION_1] and [KK] .",
